comments: Wagner (WAS) extends forward into Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path and initiates contact to Antetokounmpo's body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes brush contact with Napier's (WAS) left arm following his gather however, Napier (WAS) is able to move through the contact and finish at the rim.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) places his right arm to Wagner's (WAS) backside and extends, dislodging Wagner from his legally obtained position.
Wagner (WAS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Hill's (MIL) path and firms up when contact occurs.
Lopez (MIL) is slightly late establishing himself in Bonga's (WAS) path and although some foot-to-foot contact occurs it is marginal and Lopez does not deliver any further contact.

Middleton (MIL) makes some contact with his left forearm to Beal's (WAS) front as Beal drives inside the perimeter however, the contact is marginal and Beal (WAS) is able to move along is desired path.
Napier (WAS) does not fully establish a legal guarding position in Bledsoe's (MIL) path and initiates contact that affects Bledsoe's (MIL) SQBR.
Middleton (MIL) makes marginal contact to Wagner's (WAS) side as he receives the pass.
Lopez (MIL) places his forearm to Beal's (WAS) front during his upward shooting motion. Beal extends his right leg into Lopez's lower half thereafter and initiates further contact.
Lopez (MIL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Hachimura's (WAS) path and does not deliver the contact. Lopez (MIL) and Hachimura (WAS) briefly engage and disengage thereafter.
Wagner (WAS) makes incidental contact to the arm of Middleton (MIL) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Lopez (MIL) makes marginal body contact with Bonga (WAS) as they engage during rebounding.
Hill (MIL) makes marginal contact with Beal's (WAS) front along the perimeter however, Beal (WAS) is able to move through the contact to make his desired pass.
Lopez (MIL) makes incidental contact with Hachimura's (WAS) backside before dislodging the ball during Hachimura's shot attempt.
DiVincenzo (MIL) makes incidental contact with Bonga's (WAS) lower half during rebounding.
Lopez (MIL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Beal (WAS) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Bonga (WAS) moves laterally into Middleton's (MIL) path and initiates contact to Middleton's side prior to his gather.
Napier (WAS) turns slightly into Hill's (MIL) side as the hand-off takes place and delivers some contact, but it is marginal.
Hill (MIL) extends his right arm and makes contact with Napier's (WAS) groin area following the hand off, but the contact is incidental.
Mahinmi (WAS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Hill's (MIL) path and does not deliver contact.
Hill (MIL) briefly rests his left hand against Beal's (WAS) side and removes it as Beal (WAS) begins his upward shooting motion.
Bonga (WAS) briefly grasps Lopez's (MIL) upper half before correcting as they disengage from the pick.
Hill (MIL) and Beal (WAS) briefly engage and disengage off ball.

Mahinmi (WAS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in DiVincenzo's (MIL) path and does not deliver contact. As both players disengage from the pick, incidental foot to foot contact occurs.
Mahinmi (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Hill's (MIL) path and although some foot to foot contact occurs, the contact is marginal.
Hill (MIL) makes marginal contact with Beal's (WAS) front prior to Beal losing control of the ball on his own accord.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Beal (WAS) is the last player to touch the ball prior to the out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to the Bucks.
Middleton (MIL) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Napier's (WAS) path although incidental foot to foot contact occurs as they disengage.
Brown Jr. (WAS) and Bledsoe (MIL) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Hill (MIL) reaches in from behind and makes contact with Beal's (WAS) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Brown Jr. (WAS) commits the take foul on Middleton (MIL).
Mahinmi (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Hill's (MIL) path and slightly extends his arm into Hill's front as the screen is set, but contact is marginal.
